{"CLs":[{"__type":"IST","EID":"f509e32a-5ec0-42e6-bed5-09c82b0160ac","H":3358.7999999999997,"TXT":"(* \u000d\u000a * Version 1.3.1 :\u000d\u000a * - First major version after Eastwood and Metalworks\u000d\u000a * - Incoporates shear controls, encoder monitoring of main feeder\u000d\u000a * - added a new operations page on the HMI\u000d\u000a * - corrected a few bugs with unit conversion on encoder\u000d\u000a * - not using the calc found in the Feed_Encoder sections - now using a manual Encoder roller size set on the features HMI page\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a(*\u000d\u000a * Version 1.4.0 :\u000d\u000a * - Added straightner encoders\u000d\u000a * - Adding ABB ethercat drive for uncoiler\u000d\u000a *  ^--- Adding ethercat ACS880 variables to IO Map and toggle between sensor speed and preset speed\u000d\u000a * - Fixed a bug with coil cart forward and reverse, they were inverse of what they should be\u000d\u000a * - Added alarms so that the user knows when the coil cart cannot move because of a condition\u000d\u000a * - Changed the logic for the coil keeper so that it is only one selector\u000d\u000a * - Changed the selector logic for the pressing arm\u000d\u000a * - Redid speed control for the uncoiler ethercat drive\u000d\u000a * - Added shaker logic to C_Press, revisted the timer\u000d\u000a * - Added back in the FR3 & FR4 feedback error\u000d\u000a * - Redid the safety program\u000d\u000a * - Added uncoiler signals to ABB_ECAT\u000d\u000a * - Added IO Link sensors for feeder and uncoiler\u000d\u000a * - Added Temperature control for Etalex\u000d\u000a * - Added Off mode\u000d\u000a * - Removed the blue button as a reset button\u000d\u000a * - Made communication via ACS control for uncoiler drive possible\u000d\u000a * - Began working on auto-compensation feeder mode\u000d\u000a * - Auto compensation is working ok, need more modifications\u000d\u000a * - Modifications to the auto compensation mode\u000d\u000a * - Changed the enable switch logic\u000d\u000a * - Added signals for the safety from safety controller\u000d\u000a * - Added a speed limit to the uncoiler enable switch control\u000d\u000a * - Changed the straightner encoder mode for one with a cam \u000d\u000a * - Added Shaker Overload fault to top stop conditions\u000d\u000a * - Changed overrun verification angles\u000d\u000a * - Fixed ACS Ethercat block to output actual variables rather than using externals, added another stop code for high inertia loads\u000d\u000a * - Made sure shaker cannot start in inch mode, also added a bypass for commissioning\u000d\u000a * - Etalex temp control - inverted IO Link byte order\u000d\u000a * - Added IO Link EOM sensor to EOM alarms\u000d\u000a * - Added master axis error to motion faults\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (*\u000d\u000a * - Added servo adjustment motor\u000d\u000a * - Added shear cycles\u000d\u000a * - Added automatic shear cycles\u000d\u000a * - Two sensor option for uncoiler\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.0\u000d\u000a * - Added Abort Feed signal to UIO\u000d\u000a * - Added feed calculations\u000d\u000a * - Added die metrics and counters\u000d\u000a * - Added Auto-compensated top stop\u000d\u000a * - Added precision to the encoder in order to do smaller inch movement without start time becoming an issue\u000d\u000a * - Added speed as SPM for ECAT type drives\u000d\u000a * - Merged all recipes into one\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.0\u000d\u000a * - Added Abort Feed signal to UIO\u000d\u000a * - Added feed calculations\u000d\u000a * - Added die metrics and counters\u000d\u000a * - Added Auto-compensated top stop\u000d\u000a * - Added precision to the encoder in order to do smaller inch movement without start time becoming an issue\u000d\u000a * - Added speed as SPM for ECAT type drives\u000d\u000a * - Merged all recipes into one\u000d\u000a * - Corrections made to the original program - added safediv\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 1.6.1\u000d\u000a  * Tested and corrected various bugs related to 1.6.0\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.2\u000d\u000a * Corrected bug with standalone feeding\u000d\u000a * Adding Baumer Encoder\u000d\u000a  * Made slight modifications to the way stroke press and auto cycle works in order to prevent having an option for an external safety controller.\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 1.6.3\u000d\u000a  * Deleted ENO of SafeCAM - problem with UserIO\u000d\u000a  * Put Sharpening_Data in retained.\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a  \u000d\u000a  (* Version 1.6.4\u000d\u000a   * Corrected minor problems with contactors, overload woudln't stop the maintain contact.\u000d\u000a   * Corrected bug with the running icon when using contactors\u000d\u000a   * Made sure to prevent the press from restarting automatically if palms are maintained on the console and there is a someone in front of the curtains and then not anymore on the \u000d\u000a   * Schneider safety PLCs\u000d\u000a   * Added calc_misc to tasks\u000d\u000a   * Prevented contactors for adjustment motors from automatically restart when light curtains are let go of\u000d\u000a   * Standardized SFT signals \u000d\u000a   * Last version before servopress integration\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a(* Version 2.0.0\u000d\u000a * Adding servopress\u000d\u000a * Added an air required option for presses that require it (conventional and high tonnage servo)\u000d\u000a * Added a new CAM that uses the continue mode\u000d\u000a * Set new default values for the press retained variables\u000d\u000a * Added messages to UIO\u000d\u000a * Tested the new program, made adjustments to :\u000d\u000a \u0009\u0009Automatic single stroke, pendulum, full, UIO\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 2.1.0\u000d\u000a  * Added tonnage monitoring from Assa Abloy, integration to be tested in the future.\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a  \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.0\u000d\u000a   * Added ability to have 4 encoders on the straightner.\u000d\u000a   * Adding ability to have two HMIs\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.1\u000d\u000a   * Added ability to have linear encoders instead of cam absed ones for the straightner\u000d\u000a   * Tested most of the new features and corrected some minor bugs midway through Bluescope CTL\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a   (* Version 2.2.2\u000d\u000a    * Minor bug fixes for some items on the HMI (taken from the new instruction manual tests)\u000d\u000a\u0009* Incorporated some bug fixes from BlueScope CTL\u000d\u000a\u0009* Added ability for uncoiler to use vector speed control\u000d\u000a\u0009*)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.3\u000d\u000a   * Correcting minor bugs with Baumer encoder, defau lt value and SDOs\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.3.0\u000d\u000a   * Correcting default value in baumer encoder\u000d\u000a   * Added ability to have automatic ECAT detection\u000d\u000a   * Changed the way the loop sensor is programmed, added a proportional gain and loop sensor height from above\u000d\u000a   * Added a cut to length timer in between each cycle\u000d\u000a   * Fixed a bug with SPM and conventional press\u000d\u000a   * Prevented press from starting if not at top and there is no air pressure\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.4.0\u000d\u000a   * Added Pressing arm motor\u000d\u000a   * Modified, after a first startup on Bluescope, the new uncoiler control method\u000d\u000a   * Added Press_OUT_Press_Fault\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 2.5.0\u000d\u000a * Added a SPM for cut to lengths\u000d\u000a * Added a safety maintenance counter\u000d\u000a * Added 90 degree stop test\u000d\u000a * Made some press alarms prevent the press from restarting even when not in the top stop region\u000d\u000a * Overrun is now mandatory and the prevent start function can be bypassed but not the alarm itself\u000d\u000a * Overrun bypass will also automatically cancel itself after 12hrs\u000d\u000a * Added a transfer model information to HMI button that will transfe rall model information HMI_Press_Model_Transfer\u000d\u000a * Added conditions to the alarm that encoder is not moving if the press position is above 360\u000d\u000a * Added a timer for save data on Baumer encoders \u000d\u000a * Added overrun cam angles to HMI\u000d\u000a * Fixed a bug with user outputs where the controller would remove a cam output when trying to start because of servopress start position conditions\u000d\u000a * Added a new condition for press monitoring failure, if the overrun sensor moves while the press is idle\u000d\u000a * Added ability to change the ratio of the feeders on the HMI\u000d\u000a * Added an output to a light that would signal Automatic Single Stroke is on in front of the press\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 2.5.1\u000d\u000a  * Corrected bugs with CTL that made it so that the sequence finished after a feed rather than a shear\u000d\u000a  * Corrected a bug with CTL that prevented operation unless gag 16 was selected\u000d\u000a  * Corrected a bug with CTL that didn't reset the first feed flag when the sequence was top stopped.\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 2.5.2\u000d\u000a  * Corrected top stop bug and counter bug with shear, would stop after a feed instead of a shear. (Nailor merge fail due to folder duplication in Teams)\u000d\u000a  * Tested and corrected the SPM calc for the shear\u000d\u000a  * Corrected alarm messages on the HMI for safety alarm\u000d\u000a  * Made it so that cut to lengths show safety alarm messages\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000aVersion_Number_String := '2.5.2';\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a","W":1122.4}],"LRI":1,"RRI":2,"VLs":[]}
